| chronic\_ischemic\_hd\_initial\_prev               | initial prevalence of condition                                                                                                 | Series  | :ref:`...<CardioMetabolicDisorders-chronic_ischemic_hd_initial_prev>`     |
+----------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| interval\_between\_polls                           | months between the main polling event                                                                                           | Integer | 3                                                                         |
+----------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| pr\_bmi\_reduction                                 | probability of an individual having a reduction in BMI following weight loss treatment                                          | Real    | 0.1                                                                       |
+----------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| prob\_care\_provided\_given\_seek\_emergency\_care | The probability that correct care is fully provided to persons that have sought emergency care for a Cardio-metabolic disorder. | Real    | 0.5                                                                       |
+----------------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+---------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Contraception
=============

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Name                                                                         | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            | Type      | Value                                                   |

| Method\_Use\_In\_2010                                                        | Proportion of women using each method in 2010, by age.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Method_Use_In_2010>`            |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Pregnancy\_NotUsing\_In\_2010                                                | Probability per year of a women not on contraceptive becoming pregnant, by age.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Pregnancy_NotUsing_In_2010>`    |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Pregnancy\_NotUsing\_HIVeffect                                               | Relative probability of becoming pregnant whilst not using a a contraceptive for HIV-positive women compared to HIV-negative women.                                                                                                                                                                                                                    | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Pregnancy_NotUsing_HIVeffect>`  |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Failure\_ByMethod                                                            | Probability per month of a women on a contraceptive becoming pregnant, by method.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Failure_ByMethod>`              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| rr\_fail\_under25                                                            | The relative risk of becoming pregnant whilst using a contraceptive for woman younger than 25 years compared to older women.                                                                                                                                                                                                                           | Real      | 2.2                                                     |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Initiation\_ByMethod                                                         | Probability per month of a women who is not using any contraceptive method of starting use of a method, by method.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Initiation_ByMethod>`           |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Interventions\_Pop                                                           | Pop (population scale contraception intervention) intervention multiplier.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Interventions_Pop>`             |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Interventions\_PPFP                                                          | PPFP (post-partum family planning) intervention multiplier.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Interventions_PPFP>`            |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Initiation\_ByAge                                                            | The effect of age on the probability of starting use of contraceptive (add one for multiplicative effect).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Initiation_ByAge>`              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Initiation\_AfterBirth                                                       | The probability of a woman starting a contraceptive immidiately after birth, by method.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Initiation_AfterBirth>`         |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Discontinuation\_ByMethod                                                    | The probability per month of discontinuing use of a method, by method.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Discontinuation_ByMethod>`      |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Discontinuation\_ByAge                                                       | The effect of age on the probability of discontinuing use of contraceptive (add one for multiplicative effect).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Discontinuation_ByAge>`         |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Prob\_Switch\_From                                                           | The probability per month that a women switches from one form of contraceptive to another, conditional that she will not discontinue use of the method.                                                                                                                                                                                                | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Prob_Switch_From>`              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| Prob\_Switch\_From\_And\_To                                                  | The probability of switching to a new method, by method, conditional that the woman will switch to a new method.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-Prob_Switch_From_And_To>`       |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| days\_between\_appts\_for\_maintenance                                       | The number of days between successive family planning appointments for women that are maintaining the use of a method (for each method insorted(self.states\_that\_may\_require\_HSI\_to\_maintain\_on), i.e.[IUD, implant, injections, other\_modern, pill]).                                                                                         | List      | [4383, 1461, 91, 91, 91, 91]                            |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| age\_specific\_fertility\_rates                                              | Data table from official source (WPP) for age-specific fertility rates and calendar period.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            | Dataframe | :ref:`...<Contraception-age_specific_fertility_rates>`  |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| scaling\_factor\_on\_monthly\_risk\_of\_pregnancy                            | Scaling factor (by age-group: 15-19, 20-24, ..., 45-49) on the monthly risk of pregnancy and contraceptive failure rate. This value is found through calibration so that, at the beginning of the simulation, the age-specific monthly probability of a woman having a live birth matches the WPP age-specific fertility rate value for the same year. | List      | [1.227, 0.7191, 0.6632, 0.84945, 0.86135, 0.645, 0.941] |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| max\_number\_of\_runs\_of\_hsi\_if\_consumable\_not\_available               | The maximum number of time an HSI can run (repeats occur if the consumables are not available).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        | Integer   | 1000                                                    |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| max\_days\_delay\_between\_decision\_to\_change\_method\_and\_hsi\_scheduled | The maximum delay (in days) between the decision for a contraceptive to change and the `topen` date of the HSI that is scheduled to effect the change (when using the healthsystem).                                                                                                                                                                   | Integer   | 7                                                       |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| use\_interventions                                                           | if True: FP interventions (pop & ppfp) are simulated from the date 'interventions\_start\_date', if False: FP interventions (pop & ppfp) are not simulated.                                                                                                                                                                                            | Boolean   | False                                                   |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+
| interventions\_start\_date                                                   | The date since which the FP interventions (pop & ppfp) are implemented, if at all (ie, if use\_interventions==True                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     | Date      | 2023-01-01 00:00:00                                     |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------+

Demography
==========

+-----------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------+------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| Name                              | Description                                                   | Type       | Value                                                |
+===================================+===============================================================+============+======================================================+
| max\_age\_initial                 | The oldest age (in whole years) in the initial population     | Integer    | 120                                                  |

HealthSystem
============

+---------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+

| Daily\_Capabilities\_actual                       | The capabilities (minutes of time available of each type of officer in each facility) based on the \_estimated current\_ number and distribution of staff estimated.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     | Dataframe  | :ref:`...<HealthSystem-Daily_Capabilities_actual>`                  |

| Daily\_Capabilities\_funded                       | The capabilities (minutes of time available of each type of officer in each facility) based on the \_potential\_ number and distribution of staff estimated (i.e. those positions that can be funded).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   | Dataframe  | :ref:`...<HealthSystem-Daily_Capabilities_funded>`                  |
+---------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Daily\_Capabilities\_funded\_plus                 | The capabilities (minutes of time available of each type of officer in each facility) based on the \_potential\_ number and distribution of staff estimated, with adjustments to permit each appointment type that should be run at facility level to do so in every district.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           | Dataframe  | :ref:`...<HealthSystem-Daily_Capabilities_funded_plus>`             |
+---------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| use\_funded\_or\_actual\_staffing                 | If `actual`, then use the numbers and distribution of staff estimated to be available currently; If `funded`, then use the numbers and distribution of staff that are potentially available. If `funded\_plus`, then use a dataset in which the allocation of staff to facilities is tweaked so as to allow each appointment type to run at each facility\_level in each district for which it is defined. N.B. This parameter is over-ridden if an argument is provided to the module initialiser.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      | String     | actual                                                              |

If 'default' then use the availability specified in the ResourceFile; if 'none', then let no consumable be  ever be available; if 'all', then all consumables are always available. When using 'all' or 'none', requests for consumables are not logged. NB.
